{"tid":186566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【土地問題】(估國家)最狂套房 床、馬桶、浴室全無間隔月租2500港幣","createTime":"2017-04-04T09:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T11:21:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ec2e194ba0f0d7603ae546e108bf41f2e00de5","tid":186566,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170404/large/1491269040_5ded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170404%2Flarge%2F1491269040_5ded.jpg&h=2a168c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年04月04日<br />\n香港有土地問題，新樓單位狹小，甚至使用廁所無法關門，但台灣都有類套房，有網民近日在台北的台灣師範大學附近，發現一個面積210平方呎、月租9,800元新台幣（約2,510港元）的套房，但放眼所見只能看到馬桶和浴室，有網民笑稱，「這個價格應該就是只有馬桶和洗手台可以睡」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有網民再上傳一間套房的照片，這間套房更誇張，浴室、馬桶、洗手台都無隔間，電視甚至掛在馬桶上方，床正對的就是馬桶，有網民稱這房是在彰化縣，笑稱是「史上最狂租屋」、「虧房東想得出來」、「牢房的概念」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170404/56517307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170404%2F56517307&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=2ffa60a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170404%2F56517307&h=de2a0a50\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170404/56517307</a>"},{"pid":"f0b2c0d0dcc0d5d5de33a140a388a3b0e210f4cf","tid":186566,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"最狂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇標題已經知台灣"},{"pid":"896874807f3a480ee4040d630585aa269cba69ab","tid":186566,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c36ceb6e7d191252d5738969b7fffa5cbb808df6","tid":186566,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"本港已有：納米級劏房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/